<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">set</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;"> expandtab</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D;">           &quot; 输入 Tab 时自动转换为空格</span></span>
